OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FUnions have warned that as many as
OL,8,F50,000 people could lose their jobs
OL,9,Fand vital services could deteriorate
OL,10,Fafter Rachel Reeves confirmed plans to
OL,11,Fcut Civil Service running costs by 15%.
OL,13,FThe Chancellor said Labour was looking
OL,14,Fto cut back the Civil Service, which
OL,15,Fshe said had swelled during the Covid-
OL,16,F19 pandemic, by slashing its "back
OL,17,Foffice functions, the administrative
OL,18,Fand bureaucracy functions" by the end
OL,19,Fof this parliament.
